Biteasy,allows,users,to,search,for,data,on,the,bitcoin,network,by,block,transaction,or,address,The,Biteasy,Blockchain,API,provides,developers,with,RESTful,methods,for,reading,data,from,the,bitcoin,network,enabling,them,to,build,their,own,services,based,on,bitcoin,network,data,The,API,is,free,for,non,commercial,use,potential,commercial,users,should,contact,Biteasy